# Faz 4 — Trading Dashboard (Blazor Server)

## Mimari Karar

**Dashboard = Worker + UI (All-in-one process)**

Dashboard, hem Blazor Server UI hem de MarketDataWorker background service'ini barındırır.
Worker projesi headless (no-UI) deployment için var olmaya devam eder.

Veri akışı:
```
[Binance WebSocket]
    ↓ (MarketDataWorker)
[IMarketEventPublisher]  ← Application interface (port)
    ↓
[LiveFeedService]        ← Dashboard singleton (adapter)
    ↓ (C# events)
[Blazor Components]      ← OnInitializedAsync'de subscribe
    ↓
  InvokeAsync(StateHasChanged)
```

Worker headless (no-op publisher):
```
[Binance WebSocket]
    ↓ (MarketDataWorker)
[NullMarketEventPublisher]  ← no-op
```

